Package: my_common_functions
Type: Package
Title: Spatial Data Utilities for BC Government Workflows
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Bevan", "Ernst", 
                  email = "Bevan.Ernst@gov.bc.ca",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Utility functions for spatial data workflows including themed KML/KMZ 
    export, georeferenced PDF maps, wildlife population analysis, and spatial 
    data manipulation. Includes Lincoln-Petersen population estimates, biological 
    year calculations, movement line generation, and geometry validation tools. 
    Designed for BC Government spatial and wildlife data workflows.
